You understand and agree that all information collected via or by
              us may be transferred, processed, and stored anywhere in the
              world, including but not limited to, Singapore, China, the United
              States, the European Union, in the cloud, on our servers, on the
              servers of our affiliates, or the servers of our service
              providers, in order to provide the Services.
