Data Retention
Subject to applicable laws, rules and regulations and the fulfillment of
        our business or legal purposes, we will delete your information
        (including your personal information) promptly upon your termination of
        your account with us. We will destroy your personal information
        according to the following procedures and methods.
1.Procedures for Destruction: We select personal information subject to
        destruction and destroy them with approval of our data protection
        officer.
2.Method of Destruction: We will destroy personal information stored and
        filed electronically in a way that can be deleted by using a means that
        renders the record irrecoverable as far as possible.
