Right to data disclosure, correction, erasure or suspension of use
If you are in Japan, as a data subject, you have the right to request
        the disclosure, correction, erasure or suspension of use of your
        personal information, and we are obliged to meet your request without undue
        delay. You may send your request by email to
compliance@meitu.com
        (please quote “BeautyCam” in your email title)
or by mail to Unit 8106B,
        Level 81, International Commerce Centre, 1 Austin Road West, Kowloon,
        Hong Kong (attention: Legal Department, Meitu).
